/*
Product Requirements Document (PRD)
Village Letter Management Application

1. Product Overview
- Name: Village Letter Management System
- Purpose: To digitize and streamline the village administrative letter management process

2. Target Users
- Village administrative staff
- Village head
- Village residents

3. Core Features
3.1 User Management
- User registration and authentication
- Role-based access control (admin, staff, residents)
- User profile management

3.2 Letter Templates
- Pre-defined letter templates for common documents
- Template management system
- Custom template creation capability

3.3 Letter Processing
- Digital letter request submission
- Automated letter generation
- Letter tracking and status updates
- Digital signature integration
- Letter approval workflow

3.4 Dashboard
- Admin dashboard for monitoring
- User dashboard for tracking requests
- Analytics and reporting

4. Technical Requirements
4.1 Frontend
- Responsive web application
- Modern UI/UX design
- Cross-browser compatibility

4.2 Backend
- Secure API implementation
- Database management
- File storage system
- Authentication system

4.3 Security
- Data encryption
- Secure user authentication
- Access control
- Audit logging

5. Non-functional Requirements
- Performance: Page load time < 3 seconds
- Availability: 99.9% uptime
- Scalability: Support up to 1000 concurrent users
- Mobile responsiveness

6. Future Enhancements
- Mobile app development
- Integration with other village systems
- Advanced analytics
- Bulk processing capabilities
*/
